    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contain 是一款第一人称战术射击游戏，专注于有条理的交战、真实感与玩家选择。你可以选择离线单人游玩任务，或者与朋友组建合作小队推进进度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一个隶属于秘密组织的特种行动小队成员，负责收容外星与超自然来源的物体。每个任务都是高风险行动，需要战术规划与执行。正确的装备、站位与协同动作比反应速度更重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/891b696ada7b3e225a1fdfb7054649c6.poster.avif?t=1768948554\" width=1170 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/891b696ada7b3e225a1fdfb7054649c6.webm?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/891b696ada7b3e225a1fdfb7054649c6.mp4?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新的开始：Project Genesis</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们在 2025 年 1 月的内容更新为 Contain 带来了巨大的转变。无论你是以经验丰富的行动人员重返战场，还是第一次加入，你现在游玩的都是“重生”的 Contain，因此得名 Genesis。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于游戏代码完全从零重写，Contain:Genesis 将我们的作战能力推向极限之外。我们有从上到下彻底重建的区域，视听全面翻新，氛围强度进一步提升。你以为熟悉的任务区域如今更加令人不安，每一处阴影都隐藏着不同的威胁。Genesis 带来的改进让每一刻都更加真实、更加紧张——从你握枪的方式到你迈出的每一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/8883bd10ac709800041cde8c86ef5f4f.poster.avif?t=1768948554\" width=1170 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/8883bd10ac709800041cde8c86ef5f4f.webm?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/8883bd10ac709800041cde8c86ef5f4f.mp4?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的行动人员，你的选择</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>武器自定义</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contain 拥有 Gunsmith（枪匠），一套细致的武器改装系统。在你的武器上，你可以完全控制：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >枪管、消音器、瞄具与握把</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术附件与配件</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器操控手感与性能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个部件都有明确用途，让你按自己的玩法风格塑造武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/67a098047f5b9a900df6d5662e9e607f.poster.avif?t=1768948554\" width=1170 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/67a098047f5b9a900df6d5662e9e607f.webm?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/67a098047f5b9a900df6d5662e9e607f.mp4?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>手枪自定义</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着 Genesis，手枪也变得可自定义..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你现在可以装备诸如消音器之类的配件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色自定义</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你携带的每一发子弹、每一个医疗包、以及你选择的每一枚手雷，都会影响你在任务中作出的决定。你的装备决定交火的节奏；定义你能推进多远、何时需要冒险、以及何时必须撤退。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着 Contain: Genesis，我们的军械库进一步扩展，增加了更多武器以及用于改装它们的新部件</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/c93ae128180b133d984e91214fac69ef.poster.avif?t=1768948554\" width=1170 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/c93ae128180b133d984e91214fac69ef.webm?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/c93ae128180b133d984e91214fac69ef.mp4?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作玩法 .</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以单人游玩 Contain，也可以与最多 5 人组建一支 Fire Team。队内分工、同步移动与清晰沟通对成功完成任务至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >容错为零。友军误伤、沟通中断或站位不当都可能导致全队覆灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谨慎选择你的队伍，并提前在焕新的训练区域练习。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/d1437fb55663f167c70b2d95ee00ff77.poster.avif?t=1768948554\" width=1170 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/d1437fb55663f167c70b2d95ee00ff77.webm?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186700/extras/d1437fb55663f167c70b2d95ee00ff77.mp4?t=1768948554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备就绪，行动人员。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>降落区域已确定，目标</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>已标记。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>是时候收容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>未知了。</strong></p>",
